### E-commerce API 测试文件
### 在IDEA或VS Code(安装REST Client插件)中直接点击▶️运行

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@adminToken = Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
@userToken = Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN

###########################################################################
## 1. 用户认证接口
###########################################################################

### 用户注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "demo123456",
  "firstName": "Demo",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### 管理员登录 - 请复制返回的token到上面的adminToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 普通用户登录 - 请复制返回的token到上面的userToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "testuser",
  "password": "user123"
}

### 获取当前用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 用户登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: {{userToken}}

###########################################################################
## 2. 商品管理接口
###########################################################################

### 获取商品列表（公开）
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=0&size=10&sortBy=price&direction=asc

### 搜索商品 - 按名称
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?name=iPhone

### 搜索商品 - 按分类和价格
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?category=ELECTRONICS&minPrice=1000&maxPrice=20000

### 获取单个商品详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### 创建商品（需要管理员权限）
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPad Pro 12.9",
  "description": "M2芯片，Liquid Retina XDR显示屏",
  "price": 8999.00,
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "category": "ELECTRONICS",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/ipad.jpg"
}

### 更新商品信息（需要管理员权限）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
  "description": "256GB 深空黑色",
  "price": 8999.00,
  "stockQuantity": 45,
  "category": "ELECTRONICS"
}

### 更新商品库存（需要管理员权限）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1/stock?quantity=100
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 删除商品（软删除，标记为INACTIVE）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/2
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

###########################################################################
## 3. 订单管理接口
###########################################################################

### 创建订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {"productId": 1, "quantity": 1},
    {"productId": 3, "quantity": 2}
  ],
  "shippingAddress": {
    "recipientName": "张三",
    "addressLine1": "上海市浦东新区张江高科技园区",
    "addressLine2": "科苑路88号",
    "city": "上海",
    "state": "上海市",
    "postalCode": "201203",
    "country": "中国",
    "phoneNumber": "13900139000"
  }
}

### 获取我的订单列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/my-orders?page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 获取订单详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 取消订单
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status?status=CANCELLED
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 获取所有订单（管理员权限）
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?page=0&size=20
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 按状态筛选订单（管理员权限）
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/status/PENDING?page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

###########################################################################
## 4. 错误测试用例
###########################################################################

### 测试：用户名已存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin2@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "Test"
}

### 测试：登录密码错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 测试：未授权访问订单接口
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/my-orders

### 测试：普通用户创建商品（权限不足）
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Product",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stockQuantity": 10,
  "category": "BOOKS"
}

### 测试：库存不足的订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {"productId": 1, "quantity": 9999}
  ],
  "shippingAddress": {
    "recipientName": "Test",
    "addressLine1": "Test",
    "city": "Test",
    "state": "Test",
    "postalCode": "123456",
    "country": "Test"
  }
}
